            >Best Nurse Scheduling Software for Critical Access Hospitals (2026)</a
          >
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/blog/ukg-too-complex-small-hospital">UKG Is Too Complex for Small Hospitals: What to Use Instead</a>
        </li>
        <li>
          <a href="/blog/can-nurses-trust-ai-generated-schedule"
            >Can Nurses Trust an AI-Generated Schedule? A Fairness Audit for Small Hospitals</a
          >
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

